{"type":"message","id":"5cfb263c","parentId":"c35c877d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:20:16.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了简单的问候语\"你好\"，根据 SOUL.md 和 AGENTS.md 的要求，我需要回应每条消息，打招呼就回打招呼，简洁自然，用 emoji 点缀。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋 我是你的具身智能研究助手。今天有什么可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":66,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":10515,"totalTokens":10587,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000018480000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000019140000000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774833614790,"responseId":"msg_0000536c-babc-4b19-abcd-b61f25f1f2ef"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb23d988","parentId":"5cfb263c","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:22:12.906Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53a94acac8b0c2d8b3dacb3e9e8\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-30 09:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b53a94acac8b0c2d8b3dacb3e9e8]\nou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57: 这是我最近做的具身智能技术调研：https://otb3x42ntx.feishu.cn/wiki/Shdmw8Lmwi2R8iknQQCc8arhn6d\n我们公司打算跟韶关当地政府联合建设具身智能训练场，预计产出产品是具身训练数据，搜集具身训练场资料，帮我出个研发技术方案。"}],"timestamp":1774833732906}}
