{"type":"message","id":"7ab5ed0f","parentId":"e4f5c9ce","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:39:25.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说只是测试我能否读取飞书文档，现在我确认可以了。简单回应即可，不需要展开更多内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"哈哈，明白了！✅ 测试通过，我可以正常读取飞书文档了。\n\n以后你发任何飞书文档链接，我都能直接用 API 读取内容，不再绕弯子 📄\n\n有其他任务随时吩咐！🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":80,"cacheRead":10172,"cacheWrite":63618,"totalTokens":73876,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000022400000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000023060000000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774834753478,"responseId":"msg_8911bafe-1f63-4002-a6da-9fa42b5826e7"}}
