{"type":"message","id":"8fb7d8a1","parentId":"0ce60664","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:49:05.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我换个思路，使用飞书 API 的 batch_update 端点来更新文档内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我尝试飞书 API 的 batch_update 端点来更新文档。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2b39e32e0fb24ea0b77339b6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/OKNAwWy1bi2seckbYXKcSHqynvc/batch_update\" -H \"Authorization: Bearer t-g1043u9LUHWPZQQ7X2A7TSF7IEWUANOML627ZJD2\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\n  \"requests\": [\n    {\n      \"insert_text\": {\n        \"location\": {\"index\": 1},\n        \"text\": \"# 🤖 韶关具身智能训练场研发技术方案\\n\\n> 版本：v1.0  \\n> 日期：2026-03-30  \\n> 编制：狐狸具身智能研究助手\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 一、项目定位\\n\\n**目标**：建设华南地区首个虚实融合的具身智能训练与数据采集基地  \\n**合作方**：公司 + 韶关当地政府  \\n**核心产出**：多模态具身训练数据集 + 场景化数据服务产品  \\n**对标项目**：北京亦庄训练基地、上海张江\"麒麟\"训练场、广东省\"1+1+N\"体系\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}' 2>&1 | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":365,"cacheRead":97768,"cacheWrite":277,"totalTokens":98416,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0001022,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010286}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774835341386,"responseId":"msg_48273e35-c437-4ec8-9a05-5d21f53a5a12"}}
