{"type":"message","id":"18b58b40","parentId":"d761610f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:51:19.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我换个思路，使用飞书 API 的不同端点。可能是 API 路径不对。让我尝试使用文档的 content API 来写入。batch_update 端点似乎不存在。让我换个方式，使用逐个 block 插入的方式。先插入一个段落块。\n\n让我试试飞书 API 的 patch 方法来更新块。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我试试飞书 API 的 PATCH 方法来更新块：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4489ed3f418c4dfd8daa453f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X PATCH \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/OKNAwWy1bi2seckbYXKcSHqynvc/blocks/J5cBdupQbojdAIxBdVbcxdEqnte\" -H \"Authorization: Bearer t-g1043u9LUHWPZQQ7X2A7TSF7IEWUANOML627ZJD2\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\n  \"text\": {\n    \"elements\": [\n      {\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"# 🤖 韶关具身智能训练场研发技术方案\\n\\n版本：v1.0 | 日期：2026-03-30 | 编制：狐狸具身智能研究助手\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 一、项目定位\\n\\n目标：建设华南地区首个虚实融合的具身智能训练与数据采集基地\\n\\n合作方：公司 + 韶关当地政府\\n\\n核心产出：多模态具身训练数据集 + 场景化数据服务产品\"}}]\n  }\n}' 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":357,"cacheRead":100721,"cacheWrite":416,"totalTokens":101500,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00009996000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010062000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774835472684,"responseId":"msg_44cbaa8b-dc2e-4e5f-81fa-f48bae767668"}}
