{"type":"message","id":"ea30e37b","parentId":"d3aa156d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:51:27.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的！现在错误信息很清楚了 - 需要开通 `docx:document` 或 `docx:document:write_only` 权限。\n\n你需要给**狐狸具身智能研究助手**这个应用开通文档写入权限。\n\n**开通步骤**：\n\n1. **点击权限申请链接**（错误信息中给出的）：\n   https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a92d503982e3dbc0/auth?q=docx:document,docx:document:write_only&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\n\n2. **或者手动开通**：\n   - 访问飞书开放平台：https://open.feishu.cn/\n   - 进入「应用管理」\n   - 找到应用：**狐狸具身智能研究助手**（cli_a92d503982e3dbc0）\n   - 进入「权限管理」\n   - 申请并开通权限：`docx:document`（文档读写）\n\n3. **开通后告诉我**，我会继续写入方案内容\n\n这个权限申请需要你（或应用管理员）在飞书开放平台操作。开通后权限会立即生效，我就能继续写入文档了 🔐\n\n开通好了吗？告诉我，我继续写入剩下的内容 📝"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":281,"cacheRead":101137,"cacheWrite":718,"totalTokens":102142,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007868,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00007934}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774835480034,"responseId":"msg_d0231bde-16f5-40ea-bb2a-8295d6848e10"}}
