{"type":"message","id":"52a62f03","parentId":"8b10f90d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:54:46.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"权限似乎还没有生效，可能是因为：\n1. 应用权限需要在飞书开放平台后台点击\"发布\"才能生效\n2. 或者需要重新授权\n3. token 可能还是旧的，需要重新获取\n\n让我尝试先检查一下权限是否真的开通了，或者指导用户在开放平台上发布应用。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"权限好像还没有生效。可能是开通后需要在飞书开放平台**发布应用**才能生效。\n\n让我再尝试一个新方式 - 先用旧 token 试试看，或者需要等几分钟让权限同步。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b7007d0d26104e8685d6161b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/app_access_token/internal\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"app_id\":\"cli_a92d503982e3dbc0\",\"app_secret\":\"GowA3dw4BshEFtAhTZQlacbV1WvnfMDu\"}' 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":219,"cacheRead":102691,"cacheWrite":613,"totalTokens":103529,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006198}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774835678368,"responseId":"msg_8145a48d-c716-4ac8-af0f-5bdef875ff4c"}}
